result.reason: Server-side Group Policy issue (credential delegation settings), not an mRemoteNG bug — maintainer confirmed in 2018 and no user follow-up after triage refresh
result.approach: Server GPO 'Allow delegating saved credentials' controls this behavior; mRemoteNG uses the RDP ActiveX control which respects server authentication policy. Close as external configuration issue.
